author: Reuters
title: Italy's 5-Star Movement elects former PM Conte as leader - Reuters
description: Italy's former Prime Minister Giuseppe Conte has been  officially elected leader of the 5-Star Movement, ending months of uncertainty and division since he was first asked to head up the troubled party in February.
